#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.dt.tz_localize.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.dt.tz_localize"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:1
msgid "Localize tz-naive Datetime Array/Index to tz-aware Datetime Array/Index."
msgstr "将无时区的 Datetime Array/Index 本地化为有时区的 Datetime Array/Index。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:3
msgid ""
"This method takes a time zone (tz) naive Datetime Array/Index object and "
"makes this time zone aware. It does not move the time to another time "
"zone."
msgstr ""
"此方法接受一个无时区（tz）的 Datetime Array/Index 对象，并使其具有时区"
"信息。它不会将时间移动到另一个时区。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:7
msgid ""
"This method can also be used to do the inverse -- to create a time zone "
"unaware object from an aware object. To that end, pass `tz=None`."
msgstr "此方法也可用于反向操作——从有时区的对象创建一个无时区的对象。为此，请传入 `tz=None`。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:10
msgid ""
"Time zone to convert timestamps to. Passing ``None`` will remove the time"
" zone information preserving local time."
msgstr "要将时间戳转换到的时区。传入 ``None`` 将移除时区信息，保留本地时间。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:13
msgid ""
"When clocks moved backward due to DST, ambiguous times may arise. For "
"example in Central European Time (UTC+01), when going from 03:00 DST to "
"02:00 non-DST, 02:30:00 local time occurs both at 00:30:00 UTC and at "
"01:30:00 UTC. In such a situation, the `ambiguous` parameter dictates how"
" ambiguous times should be handled.  - 'infer' will attempt to infer fall"
" dst-transition hours based on   order - bool-ndarray where True "
"signifies a DST time, False signifies a   non-DST time (note that this "
"flag is only applicable for   ambiguous times) - 'NaT' will return NaT "
"where there are ambiguous times - 'raise' will raise an "
"AmbiguousTimeError if there are ambiguous   times."
msgstr ""
"当时钟因夏令时（DST）回退时，可能会出现歧义时间。例如在中欧时间（UTC+01）"
"中，从 03:00 DST 回退到 02:00 非 DST 时，02:30:00 的本地时间可能同时出现"
"在 00:30:00 UTC 和 01:30:00 UTC。在这种情况下，`ambiguous` 参数决定如何"
"处理歧义时间。  - 'infer' 将尝试根据顺序推断秋季 DST 转换小时  - bool-"
"ndarray，其中 True 表示 DST 时间，False 表示非 DST 时间（注意该标志仅适用"
"于歧义时间）  - 'NaT' 将在出现歧义时间处返回 NaT  - 'raise' 会在出现歧义"
"时间时引发 AmbiguousTimeError"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:13
msgid ""
"When clocks moved backward due to DST, ambiguous times may arise. For "
"example in Central European Time (UTC+01), when going from 03:00 DST to "
"02:00 non-DST, 02:30:00 local time occurs both at 00:30:00 UTC and at "
"01:30:00 UTC. In such a situation, the `ambiguous` parameter dictates how"
" ambiguous times should be handled."
msgstr ""
"当由于夏令时导致时钟向后移动时，可能会出现时间歧义。例如在中欧时间（UTC+"
"01）中，从03:00夏令时转换到02:00非夏令时时，02:30:00本地时间会在00:30:00 "
"UTC和01:30:00 UTC两个时刻都出现。在这种情况下，`ambiguous`参数决定了应该"
"如何处理这些时间歧义。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:20
msgid "'infer' will attempt to infer fall dst-transition hours based on order"
msgstr "'infer' 将尝试根据顺序推断秋季 dst-转换小时"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:22
msgid ""
"bool-ndarray where True signifies a DST time, False signifies a non-DST "
"time (note that this flag is only applicable for ambiguous times)"
msgstr ""
"bool-ndarray，其中 True 表示 DST 时间，False 表示非 DST 时间（注意该标志"
"仅适用于歧义时间）"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:25
msgid "'NaT' will return NaT where there are ambiguous times"
msgstr "'NaT' 将在出现歧义时间处返回 NaT"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:26
msgid "'raise' will raise an AmbiguousTimeError if there are ambiguous times."
msgstr "'raise' 会在出现歧义时间时引发 AmbiguousTimeError。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:29
msgid ""
"A nonexistent time does not exist in a particular timezone where clocks "
"moved forward due to DST.  - 'shift_forward' will shift the nonexistent "
"time forward to the   closest existing time - 'shift_backward' will shift"
" the nonexistent time backward to the   closest existing time - 'NaT' "
"will return NaT where there are nonexistent times - timedelta objects "
"will shift nonexistent times by the timedelta - 'raise' will raise an "
"NonExistentTimeError if there are   nonexistent times."
msgstr ""
"在特定时区中，由于 DST 时钟向前调整，某些时间可能并不存在。  - 'shift_"
"forward' 会将不存在的时间向前移动到最近的现有时间  - 'shift_backward' 会"
"将不存在的时间向后移动到最近的现有时间  - 'NaT' 会在存在不存在的时间处"
"返回 NaT  - timedelta 对象会根据 timedelta 移动不存在的时间  - 'raise' 会"
"在出现不存在的时间时引发 NonExistentTimeError"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:29
msgid ""
"A nonexistent time does not exist in a particular timezone where clocks "
"moved forward due to DST."
msgstr "不存在的时间在特定时区中不存在，当时钟因 DST 向前移动时。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:32
msgid ""
"'shift_forward' will shift the nonexistent time forward to the closest "
"existing time"
msgstr "'shift_forward' 将不存在的时间向前移动到最接近的 存在时间"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:34
msgid ""
"'shift_backward' will shift the nonexistent time backward to the closest "
"existing time"
msgstr "'shift_backward' 将不存在的时间向后移动到最接近的 存在时间"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:36
msgid "'NaT' will return NaT where there are nonexistent times"
msgstr "'NaT' 将在存在不存在时间处返回 NaT"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:37
msgid "timedelta objects will shift nonexistent times by the timedelta"
msgstr "timedelta 对象将通过 timedelta 移动不存在的时间"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:38
msgid "'raise' will raise an NonExistentTimeError if there are nonexistent times."
msgstr "'raise' 会在存在不存在时间时引发 NonExistentTimeError。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:42
msgid "Array/Index converted to the specified time zone."
msgstr "已转换到指定时区的 Array/Index。"

