msgid ":py:obj:`DatetimeIndex.tz_convert`"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:50
msgid "Convert tz-aware DatetimeIndex from one time zone to another."
msgstr "将有时区信息的 DatetimeIndex 从一个时区转换到另一个时区。"

