msgid "Localize DatetimeIndex in US/Eastern time zone:"
msgstr "将 DatetimeIndex 本地化到 US/Eastern 时区："

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:71
msgid ""
"With the ``tz=None``, we can remove the time zone information while "
"keeping the local time (not converted to UTC):"
msgstr "使用 ``tz=None``，我们可以移除时区信息并保留本地时间（不会转换为 UTC）："

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:79
msgid ""
"Be careful with DST changes. When there is sequential data, pandas can "
"infer the DST time:"
msgstr "小心DST变化。当有连续数据时，pandas可以推断DST时间："

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:99
msgid ""
"In some cases, inferring the DST is impossible. In such cases, you can "
"pass an ndarray to the ambiguous parameter to set the DST explicitly"
msgstr ""
"在某些情况下，推断DST是不可能的。在这种情况下，您可以将ndarray传递给"
"ambiguous参数来显式设置DST"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:111
msgid ""
"If the DST transition causes nonexistent times, you can shift these dates"
" forward or backwards with a timedelta object or `'shift_forward'` or "
"`'shift_backwards'`."
msgstr ""
"如果DST转换导致不存在的时间，您可以使用timedelta对象或'shift_forward'或'"
"shift_backwards'将这些日期向前或向后移动。"

